{"tid":1856533,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人喺台北旅行買到一盒盒既口罩？","createTime":"2020-02-01T16:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T09:34:00.000Z","uid":319969,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f884a32af23b9ecc38924655dc302b4dd28013","tid":1856533,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:24:24.000Z","msg":"我依家喺台北<br />\n今日6,7點起身撲口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行咗N間便利店都話今日冇補貨<br />\n行過啲藥房又話賣晒<br />\n依家康是美同屈臣氏會賣每人3個口罩<br />\n2個人瘋狂走囇好多間先買到18個<br />\n依家屋企啲口罩倒數緊(20個左右 3個人用)<br />\n打算買足佢個限額分俾身邊同樣赤貧既朋友<br />\n有無人喺台北旅行買到一盒盒嘅口罩？<br />\n可唔可以話我知係邊度買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3號翻香港<br />\n<br />\n依家喺台灣一日用一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打算留翻喺香港先用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51de801ca75702efadb64def2a560be3d24eb211","tid":1856533,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想死住呀~"},{"pid":"2e2c8aab79899409bb51fbf25dc20f438d26cdf4","tid":1856533,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3575b7e1d4569c73a414e0500e121c98012dd91","tid":1856533,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2e2c8aab79899409bb51fbf25dc20f438d26cdf4","tid":1856533,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fec4eb2f7aaa9cc0484c649d6dc39ea5eb7cef2","tid":1856533,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3575b7e1d4569c73a414e0500e121c9801