ore":0,"quote":{"pid":"2618241bd8ac5a3048897cb0caaf3ab6c4dd1889","tid":1856533,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"而家2 月喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過年成個台灣都無盒裝醫療口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"仲有人覺得會有所謂既大貨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"有大貨到呀<br />\n我今日見啲藥妝同百貨店都有盒裝買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該開始多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"有咩？喺邊，完全唔見有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43787f179f86619c41ab0fc500ddbf369b278f85","tid":1856533,"uid":105592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"今日行哂成個北車同後站都冇，間間都貼哂話賣哂<br />\n我咁啱過路一間返貨先買到三個呢幾日喺台北用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fc996880be26e4379c35a798f6c9a0ff34af28","tid":1856533,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DA1dTY6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDA1dTY6.png&h=52009836&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBBp0Ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBBp0Ec.png&h=85a62a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我1點去買<br />\n店員話有50盒<br />\n我只係買咗一盒<br />\n因為已經夠用所以留翻俾啲台灣人<br />\n&bull;<br />\n西門站6號出口隔離嗰間藥妝都有一盒盒既口罩賣<br />\n&bull;<br />\n饒河街夜市有間雜貨店有<br />\n格局大約係咁<br />\n賣啲內衣褲 襪之類既野<br />\n佢掛喺個架度<br />\n你問佢就有<br />\n但係我唔敢買好多<br />\n一黎佢係幼童size<br />\n二黎唔知咩規格 有冇bfe嗰啲<br />\n好單純一個包裝(見下圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNyvWeS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNyvWeS.jpg&h=2035d001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4vaWgd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4vaWgd.png&h=9008717d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ev3G2Wj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fev3G2Wj.png&h=9d96d48a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&bull;<br />\n有巴打話大醫院出邊嘅販賣機有得賣<br />\n有係有但係可能對我地來講太遠<br />\n每人只可以買一盒 <br />\n而且一盒得兩個<br />\n&bull;<br />\n除咗便利店有得買口罩之外<br />\n康是美同屈臣氏都有<br />\n&bull;<br />\n可以去藥房或者一啲買醫療用品嘅店問吓<br />\n佢哋都可能有<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e360c3e6ee5500babc2b0b72ee93cb079b2923a","tid":1856533,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43787f179f86619c41ab0fc500ddbf369b278f85","tid":1856533,"uid":105592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"今日行哂成個北車同後站都冇，間間都貼哂話賣哂<br />\n我咁啱過路一間返貨先買到三個呢幾日喺台北用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"放咗資料上嚟<br />\n希望你買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11be7a9b72ca1b99d6383c4da7b38374546f3ceb","tid":1856533,"uid":105592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e360c3e6ee5500babc2b0b72ee93cb079b2923a","tid":1856533,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43787f179f86619c41ab0fc500ddbf369b278f85","tid":1856533,"uid":105592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"今日行哂成個北車同後站都冇，間間都貼哂話賣哂<br />\n我咁啱過路一間返貨先買到三個呢幾日喺台北用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"放咗資料上嚟<br />\n希望你買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"感謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我台灣朋友都話買唔到<br />\n我唔想再搵，好 stressed, 開開心心去玩食下野就算"},{"pid":"64a6e3b5008af0297fc15c5c25eddf73f3adce0c","tid":1856533,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11be7a9b72ca